    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some thinning paint on the hood and roof, while the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and some fading on the dashboard plastics. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, but you should expect to address some minor fluid leaks and upcoming suspension maintenance in the near future. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic character and a few weekend DIY projects.",
      "price": 18500.0,
