    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Demonstrating consistent mechanical excellence and a well-preserved aesthetic, it offers a refined driving experience characterized by both poise and performance. Each aspect of the vehicle has been thoroughly vetted to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for quality and sustained reliability on the road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
